  }
  user_input {
    user_response: "System Role & ObjectiveAct as an expert Full-Stack Software Engineer. Your task is to build a Minimum Viable Product (MVP) for a web application named \"whisp\". It is a 100% anonymous, zero-login, and ephemeral global social media platform where all posts automatically delete after 24 hours.Tech Stack RequirementsMust use the Cloudflare free-tier ecosystem:Frontend: SvelteKit deployed on Cloudflare Pages for a lightweight and mobile-optimized application.Backend / API: Hono.js on Cloudflare Workers for ultra-fast, lightweight routing.Database (Main Data): Cloudflare D1 (SQLite at the edge) for structured post data.Database (Key-Value): Cloudflare KV for strict rate-limiting and preventing interaction spam.Automation: Cloudflare Cron Workers scheduled every hour to purge expired posts.UI & UX Design SystemTheme: Strict monochrome (Black and White).Dark Mode: Include an inversion toggle for dark mode (White text on Black background).Layout & Styling: Use Tailwind CSS to create a mobile-first, responsive, and minimalistic linear feed.Post Component: Each post must be rendered as a standalone \"Card\".Card Elements: The card must include the generated avatar color, anonymous author name, text content, UP/DOWN buttons, and an explicit countdown timer (e.g., \"Disappears in 21h 14m\") to drive FOMO.Database Schema (Cloudflare D1)Create a single table named posts with the following structure:ColumnTypeDescriptionidString8-character unique identifier (Nanoid).contentTextThe post content, maximum 500 characters.author_nameStringThe daily generated Babel name using native scripts.author_tokenStringHMAC hash of the user\'s IP + Daily Salt.up_countIntegerCounter for UP interactions, default 0.down_countIntegerCounter for DOWN interactions, default 0.created_atTimestampStandard creation timestamp.expires_atTimestampSet exactly to created_at + 24 hours.reply_toStringNullable, contains id of another post if replying.Core Mechanics & Logic1. Anonymous Identity Engine (Babel System)Do not store user IPs. Generate a unique daily identity for users using this logic:Create a token using the formula:$$\\text{Token Unik} = \\text{HMAC-SHA256}(\\text{IP Public} + \\text{Secret Salt} + \\text{Tanggal Hari Ini})$$Use the token to deterministically select: an Emoji, an Adjective, and a Noun from an array containing words in 10 different native scripts (e.g., English, Chinese, Korean, Arabic, Russian).Extract 6 hex characters from the token to generate a valid hex color code (e.g., #FF5733) for the user\'s avatar background or name highlight.Use the HTML <bdi> tag to isolate text directions and prevent RTL/LTR rendering issues in the UI.2. Interaction Engine (UP & DOWN)UP Button: Boosts the post\'s visibility.DOWN Button: Lowers the post\'s visibility and acts as a report mechanism.Spam Protection: When an interaction occurs, write a key interact:postID:authorToken to Cloudflare KV. Deny any further interaction on the same post by the same token.Auto-Hide Moderation: If up_count - down_count equals -5, automatically hide the post from the main feed.3. Feed Algorithm (Gravity Score)Sort the main feed dynamically by calculating a gravity score. Use this mathematical formula for the sorting query:\n$$\\text{Score} = \\frac{\\text{UP} - \\text{DOWN}}{(\\text{Age in Hours} + 2)^G}$$Set the gravity constant (G) to 1.8.This ensures brand new posts appear near the top, but older posts require substantial UP interactions to maintain their position."
